OL,4,C#100,000 in Wagatha costs battle
OL,6,FLegal wrangling continues over the
OL,7,Fcost of the Wagatha Christie case as
OL,8,FITV News Correspondent Geraint Vincent
OL,9,Fexplains
OL,11,FRebekah Vardy has been ordered to pay
OL,12,FColeen Rooney a further #100,000
OL,13,Ffollowing their high-profile Wagatha
OL,14,FChristie libel battle ahead of the
OL,15,Ffull amount owed being decided.
OL,17,FBarristers for the two have appeared
OL,18,Fin court in a dispute over legal costs
OL,19,Fafter Mrs Vardy lost her High Court
OL,20,Fclaim against Mrs Rooney in 2022.
