OL,6,FIt followed Mrs Rooney accusing Mrs
OL,7,FVardy of leaking her private
OL,8,Finformation to the press on social
OL,9,Fmedia, with Wednesday marking five
OL,10,Fyears since the viral social media
OL,11,Fpost at the heart of the dispute.
OL,13,FMrs Vardy was later ordered to pay 90%
OL,14,Fof Mrs Rooney's fees, with an initial
OL,15,Fpayment of #800,000.
OL,17,FBut at the end of the hearing, which
OL,18,Fbegan on Monday, senior costs judge
OL,19,FAndrew Gordon-Saker ordered Mrs Vardy
OL,20,Fto pay a further #100,000 to Mrs
OL,21,FRooney within 21 days.
