OL,4,C#100,000 in Wagatha costs battle
OL,6,FHe said: "I think there is some scope
OL,7,Ffor a further payment on account so
OL,8,Fthe defendant (Mrs Rooney) is not kept
OL,9,Fout of her costs, and I think that
OL,10,Fshould be no more than #100,000."
