OL,6,FThe hearing, which neither woman
OL,7,Fattended, dealt with several
OL,8,Fpreliminary issues before a full "line-
OL,9,Fby-line" assessment of costs takes
OL,10,Fplace at a later date, which will
OL,11,Fdecide the overall amount of money to
OL,12,Fbe paid.
OL,14,FJudge Gordon-Saker said this could
OL,15,Ftake place in early 2025, but added:
OL,16,F"The parties need to get on with this
OL,17,Fand put it behind them."
